---
// Hero.astro - Wersja Kinowa z nowoczesnym Social Proof
---

<section id="hero" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="sr-only">
    <h2>Ekspert Business Intelligence – Usługi Power BI i Usługi Excel</h2>
    <p>
      Specjalizujemy się w: tworzenie arkuszy Excel, automatyzacja raportów, 
      wdrażanie Power BI Katowice, naprawa plików Excel oraz profesjonalne 
      dashboardy menedżerskie.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img 
      src="/biuro3.webp" 
      alt="Nowoczesne biuro analizy danych Power BI i Excel" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover scale-105 animate-slow-pan"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/75"></div> <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-950 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute -top-1/4 -right-1/4 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-green-500/10 rounded-full blur-[160px] animate-pulse"></div>
  </div>


  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 pt-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl">
      
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md">
        <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#22c55e]"></span>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-300">Data Excellence & Automation</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-[1.1] lg:leading-[0.95]">
        Profesjonalne dashboardy <br/>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-green-600">Power BI</span> 
        i automatyzacja <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-green-600">Excel.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Zamieniamy chaos w arkuszach na przejrzyste raporty. Oferujemy specjalistyczne 
        <strong class="text-white">usługi Power BI</strong> oraz profesjonalne 
        <strong class="text-white">tworzenie arkuszy Excel</strong>. 
        Oszczędzaj do <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">20h tygodniowo</span>.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 mb-20">
        <a href="#kontakt" class="group bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-500 text-white py-5 px-10 rounded-2xl font-black text-xl shadow-2xl shadow-green-600/30 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
          Umów darmowy audyt
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-sm transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="#demo" class="bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white py-5 px-10 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl border border-white/20 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <i class="fas fa-play text-green-500"></i>
          Zobacz demo
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green-500/20 blur-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
          <div class="relative flex items-center gap-5 p-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/20 to-green-600/5 flex items-center justify-center border border-green-500/20 shadow-inner">
              <i class="fas fa-project-diagram text-green-500 text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-black text-white leading-none">100+</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-widest mt-2">Wdrożonych projektów</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green-500/20 blur-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
          <div class="relative flex items-center gap-5 p-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/20 to-green-600/5 flex items-center justify-center border border-green-500/20 shadow-inner">
              <i class="fas fa-hourglass-half text-green-500 text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-black text-white leading-none">20h+</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-widest mt-2">Odzyskanych tygodniowo</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green-500/20 blur-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
          <div class="relative flex items-center gap-5 p-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/20 to-green-600/5 flex items-center justify-center border border-green-500/20 shadow-inner">
              <i class="fas fa-star text-green-500 text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex gap-1 mb-1">
                <i class="fas fa-star text-green-500 text-[10px]"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star text-green-500 text-[10px]"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star text-green-500 text-[10px]"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star text-green-500 text-[10px]"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star text-green-500 text-[10px]"></i>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xl font-black text-white leading-none">Ekspert 5.0</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-widest mt-2">Średnia ocena klientów</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute right-10 bottom-10 hidden lg:block">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
      <div class="w-px h-24 bg-gradient-to-t from-green-500 to-transparent"></div>
      <span class="[writing-mode:vertical-lr] text-slate-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em] font-bold">Zjedź niżej</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes slow-pan {
    0% { transform: scale(1.05) translate(0, 0); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.1) translate(-1%, -1%); }
    100% { transform: scale(1.05) translate(0, 0); }
  }
  .animate-slow-pan {
    animation: slow-pan 20s linear infinite;
  }
</style>